<item>
            <title>[WICKET-4103] FeedbackMessages added in IRequestCycleListener#onRequestHandlerExecuted do not get displayed in response page</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-4103</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When adding a feedback message in IRequestCycleListener#onRequestHandlerExecuted it does not get displayed on the response page. It is also not available on subsequent requests. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>WinXP SP2, Eclipse 3.4.2</environment>
